Â· Visually inspect the interior and undercarriage of vehicles entering parking lots and terraces.
Â· Deploy equipment assets and ensure physical security measures be afforded to them at critical sites.
Â· Assemble trained volunteers to include: CERT, COP, ARES and the American Red Cross.
Â· Implement Mutual Aid Agreements as required.
