Â· Take appropriate action to protect them by deploying armed security forces to these sites.
Â· Cancel or delay unnecessary employee travel and leave.
Â· Activate the Emergency Operations Center.
Â· Control release of information to the public and news media.
Â· Send a Public Information Officer to the state Joint Information Center (JIC).
Â· Provide security for personnel dispatched to repair or restore damaged facilities and systems.
