Â· Continue all precautions from lower Threat Conditions.
Â· Deny all access to all public buildings and other critical infrastructure except to those authorized.
Â· Inspect all packages, vehicles, and authorized personnel entering public buildings and other critical infrastructure.
Â· Place all law enforcement critical resources on restricted stand by in the affected areas.
Â· Cancel all employee leave.
Â· Provide staffing to the Emergency Operations Center.
Â· Through the Public Information Center, manage information released to the public ensuring coordination with other public safety and Chief Administrative/Elected Officials.
